description: Columbus’ oldest ice cream company has been treating the locals to delicious scoops of quality flavor since way back in 1950. Thanks to this mobile trailer (AKA “The Big Dipper”), you and your friends can enjoy these delightfully creamy family recipes right at your next event!Butter Fudge Swirl, Praline Pecan, and Raspberry Cheesecake are only a few of the wonderful flavors you’ll find along with all your favorite classics. They’re dishing out scrumptious frozen yogurts, sherbets, and sorbets too! If you’re craving really tasty real ice cream, Johnson’s has got just the scoop for you!
name: Johnson's Real Ice Cream
